name: Being There - Just What We Do

metadata.description:
As rumors swirl and bitches brew, so it goes that tim and chloe return to reclaim what is rightfully theirs. A blood lust, a far away moon, something sentimental and something just out of reach. Fuck around, nothin heavy its just what we do.  

We made this song in the summer and had not a care in the fucking world. "thats not a second verse" they said.  Just let your head unscrew itself and stop pretending to know anything. now THATS a great idea!!!!

Being There
